<paragraph base="F29577472" id="IFRS14_26"><paranum>26</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 14"/><data name="paranum" value="26"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS14_P0067">When an entity presents earnings per share in accordance with <xref base="F33213248" href="../ias33/IAS33_TOC.dita#IAS33_TOC0001" id="IFRS14_X0118"><ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_number">IAS 33</ph> <ph outputclass="standard_title">Earnings per Share</ph></ph></xref>, the entity shall present additional basic and diluted earnings per share, which are calculated using the earnings amounts required by IAS 33 but excluding the movements in <xref base="F29577655" href="IFRS14_APPA.dita#IFRS14_APPA/IFRS14_DI0007">regulatory deferral account balances<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0321"/></ph></xref> (see <xref base="F33213268" href="IFRS14_gB13-B14.dita#IFRS14_gB13-B14" id="IFRS14_X0119">paragraphs B13&#x2013;B14</xref>).</p></body></paragraph>